# Cursor MCP — regenerate after git pull

Tracked [.cursor/mcp.json](../../.cursor/mcp.json) commits **glossary-knowledge only** (sibling paths).  
**techsapo-providers**, **serena**, and **brv** (ByteRover; successor to legacy Cipher) use machine-local absolute paths and are **not** preserved across `git pull`.

## Mandatory after every `git pull`

```bash
npm run build && npm run cursor-mcp:config
```

Then: Cursor **Settings → MCP → Reload**.

## When to run again

- Serena, brv, or techsapo-providers missing from MCP list
- `package.json` / MCP scripts / generator changed on pull
- Node path or clone location changed on this machine

Full procedure: [CURSOR_MCP_TEMPLATE.md](../../docs/CURSOR_MCP_TEMPLATE.md) · [commands.md](../../docs/agents/commands.md)
